data.description: The entryway welcomes you home as you walk in the spacious vaulted ceilings.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1704 sq foot home floor plan offers multi use spaces to arrange in a way that suites your needs.  Large living area with large windows facing the front yard.  Nook area perfect for a little office area or formal dining. Secondary area that could be perfect for a TV room or flex space.  Dining/breakfast nook arranged perfectly adjacent to the kitchen that offers knotty cabinets eat at bar that makes for tons of countertop space.  Wrap around hallway makes for easy access to the laundry and attached oversized garage as well as the spare bedrooms.  2 oversized linen closets in the hallway.  Large oversized primary bedroom with walk in closet and on suite.  Fully fenced backyard, forced air furnace, located near schools, parks and shopping.   Seller is offering a $3,000 credit towards paint/flooring. Call your Realtor today to schedule your personal tour!
